sql:
SELECT shipping_method
FROM shipping_options
WHERE cost = (SELECT MIN(cost) FROM shipping_options);

SELECT MAX(stock_quantity) AS max_stock_quantity
FROM item_sizes
WHERE item_id = 0 AND size_id = 1;

external_knowledge:
- Top three sizes refer to the sizes with the highest total sales quantity in each category;
- Sales quantity refers to the total quantity of items ordered;
- Categories refer to the types of clothing items, such as T-shirts, Pants, etc.
